title: What happened when Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez came face to face with Facebook’s Mark Zuckerberg
text: It was 1am the night before we published the Cambridge Analytica files in March last year and I got an urgent message from my fellow reporter, Emma Graham-Harrison. Facebook, which that day had sent us a letter threatening legal action if we published, had issued a press release saying it had kicked Cambridge Analytica off its platform.
